We're building a simple crud application to manipulate persons  using angular .
1) Fake json server   : 1. install it npm install -g json-server , 
                       2.make a db.json file for the mock data ,
                       3.navigate to db.json file and run the command : json-server --watch db.json
                       4.http://localhost:3000/persons should return the fake data now. we can preform all crud operations on this fake server.
                       5.for more info go to -> https://github.com/typicode/json-server
2) Add bootstrap :  1. npm install bootstrap
                    2. update angular.json 
                    3.restart app
3) generate new components : add , edit and list
4) Work on the user interface for the diffrent components and build the routing.
5) Make the Person interface 
6) Generate a personService that holds the crud operations with our api
7) inject the service in our components one by one and test 


                 